Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.55,0:01:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 围住他了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.07,0:01:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易恢复意识 却如此狼狈…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不好对付啊 帕库拉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕库拉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.62,0:02:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.14,0:02:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经忍无可忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.29,0:02:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心我毫不留情地来个大爆炸啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕吗 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.98,0:02:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了防止你爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经准备好雷遁伺候了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少吹牛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哑火的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艺术是不会哑火的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道要爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:02:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是有人成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人柱力们好像要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来鼬果然成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了 鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边还没什么进展
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别废话了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我转告大野木
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待守护忍者联军至最后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来向我汇报吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个阴谋家被摆平了吗…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后还是哑火了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽吓唬人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是哑火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艺术是永恒的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又吓唬人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来终于能摆脱这可恨的诅咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕库拉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧 不要死得太随意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还有未来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来终于能彻彻底底地死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勘九郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傀儡师的技艺就托付给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会传承下去的…千代婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下再也没法装死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出所料…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经恢复自主意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我解开结界 丁座…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 已经不需要结界了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丁座…不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个印是灵化术吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧去纲手大人那儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个杀戮了无数忍者的术…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟能发挥这样的作用…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵化之术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除秽土转生后升天的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以利用灵化术来控制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过看来时间有限
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了 丁座
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:06:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉…厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以灵体的样子直接飞走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵化术到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是能将施术者灵体化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无视距离附身于敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并将其诛杀的术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了村子的未来 必须进行改革
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是为了能减少牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否助我一臂之力呢 纲手…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不嫌弃我的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起实现梦想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者的梦想…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底…是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些秽土转生者的查克拉正一个接一个地消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各地部队发来报告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秽土转生者们正在升天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被封印的 以及还在活动的都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这个状况来判断
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是秽土转生被解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秽土转生被解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我将消息传达给所有的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总部有消息传达
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秽土转生被解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秽土转生被解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秽土转生的部队正在消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…到底是哪支部队做到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便你永远不原谅我也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:09:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你今后如何选择…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都会一直爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由木人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢仓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗形
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胡子叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.61,0:10:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来…其他战场也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜那个混蛋…失败了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开小差了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的对手可是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.63,0:10:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我苍兰的猛兽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来秽土转生被解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又…如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那道光芒…到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须佐能乎消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秽土转生的尘埃也在飞舞飘扬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秽土转生被解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还在搜寻兜的所在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅发现了他 连忍术都阻止了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是谁 他都是守护了忍者世界的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来老天爷还没抛弃我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你们那边也有厉害的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备去死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来打算在消失之前来个最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火遁.龙炎放歌之术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水遁…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百豪术耗尽了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…赢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该完全失去意识了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.05,0:12:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明动弹不得 怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久不见了 是我啊 纲手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是断啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断 你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秽土转生被解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 我就用灵化术飞了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过刚才真危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一点都没变呢 纲手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断 我一直对…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间有限
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顾不上伤感了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能逗留片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断战斗 不断失去最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并不是忍者的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢村子和同伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想守护他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为能守护大家的火影…是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断 你死后我一直都在逃避对你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.87,0:14:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今你的遗憾以及曾想完成的夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够再度实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已成为了火影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 纲手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经很努力地替我完成了理想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你背负了很多痛苦的回忆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会在那边等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不要太早来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的时刻还能保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回的秽土转生也算有些价值了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影 你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你恢复意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人给你查克拉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和故人叙叙旧而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就会重逢的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑的查克拉在脱离肉体之际又悉数返回
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复了原样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么没有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秽土转生应该被解除了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秽土转生是用来召唤死者的通灵术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有一个风险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是只要知道结印
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被转生的死者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:16:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能解除秽土转生的通灵契约
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除契约
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切就简单多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死之身 无限的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不受施术者的制约 随意行动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉施术者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁术切勿滥用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秽土转生 解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何谓家族
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何谓村子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何谓忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里干吗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止秽土转生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没打算向别人解释清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过都好久没见了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是详细解释一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:17:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他使用了秽土转生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种…这种事 可能吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的忍术 怎能可能束缚得了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为我的对手 你们应该不意外吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 关于须佐能乎的完全体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说领教过的人难逃一死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前用了一次 不了了之
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次就太难堪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被干扰了 真扫兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该去抓九尾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的斑就交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会做个了断的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.73,0:19:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土影大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经不是我们能匹敌的对手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此也要拼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须就此阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷传
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招 小指攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸色似乎不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此话怎讲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:20:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为脸被挡住了 所以我随便猜的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不爽的话就摘下面具
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看你那故作冷静的脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说别刺激对手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能动手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大的葫芦和壶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本想让其以完全的姿态复活的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只是碎片 但力量不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该践行诺言了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.35,0:22:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,知道一切的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,有个人我必须去见一见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.35,0:22:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.47,0:22:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.64,0:22:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.35,0:22:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,下集 火影忍者疾风传
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.22,0:22:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,复活 大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.20,0:23:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,鸣坂46 修行中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.34,0:23:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,那句“若能不言语 放声哭泣就好”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.20,0:23:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.82,0:23:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,那段我正好想到鸣人了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.96,0:23:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,“真正的孤独  乃抛弃曾经 专注今时之人”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.04,0:23:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,超级酷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.05,0:23:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,真帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fnsimhei\fs22\pos(170,375)}主题歌《月亮的大小》中\N{\r}{\fsp10\fnsimhei\fs22}喜欢的歌词是